{"tid":27840,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"YouTube2016年排行榜正式出爐!!!","createTime":"2016-12-07T14:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T06:33:42.000Z","uid":31447,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5cd14e99af4cc1917f8341acada9c3e5ebc2e5f","tid":27840,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:45:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161207/mobile/bkntw-20161207171244369-1207_04511_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20161207%2Fmobile%2Fbkntw-20161207171244369-1207_04511_001.html&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTz0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=d4380fe4\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20161207/mobile/bkntw-20161207171244369-1207_04511_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTz0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=c89acafd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】YouTube香港剛剛公布2016年度熱門影片排行榜，隨着本地Youtuber愈來愈受歡迎，入榜的幾乎都是由他們創作。年度十大熱門原創影片排行榜中，又名「熊仔頭」的本地影音創作者、有超過40萬訂閱的FHProductionHK有三段片入榜，當中「我在香港分手的日子 - 上集」中大談男性在分手時的無奈和痛苦，成功引起網民對兩性相處的激烈討論，打入原創影片排行榜之首。另一人氣創作人笑波子也打入排行榜，他將PIKO太郎的洗腦神曲「PPAP」製造成二創影片「REAL Pen Pineapple Apple Pen (PPAP)」，笑死一班網民而進佔原創影片排行榜第四位。 <br />\n<br />\n非本地原創影片排行榜方面，結果估你唔到，十大中有七段是由台灣網路紅人谷阿莫創作，他以獨特見解分析電影及電視劇重點，今年就有講解古裝網路電視劇《太子妃升職記》榮登榜首，談及香港電影《陀地驅魔人》人榜也位列第三。 <br />\n<br />\n音樂影片方面，今年是華語及廣東話音樂影片的天下，本地人氣樂隊Dear Jane以廣東歌《哪裡只得我共你》登上YouTube香港2016年度十大熱門音樂影片排行榜榜首，其他還包括台灣天王周杰倫及天后張惠妹合唱的《不該》、周興哲為連續劇《遺憾拼圖》演唱的片尾曲的《你，好不好？》，以及樂壇新人JC的《說散就散》等等。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b48O91i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb48O91i.jpg&h=ca5013c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0z6bY27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0z6bY27.jpg&h=47a14961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YqW4a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YqW4a6.jpg&h=f7bf2596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6dja2w1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6dja2w1.jpg&h=2a7c6979&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30618caee89b867b8a607a0af37b52e43da3a165","tid":27840,"uid":15086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"熊仔頭同Bomba真係年年玩哂<br />\n無港女之歌矛盾一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9735bd7c3cc8cd2cc73ada0fa9b7571e25d9d9f9","tid":27840,"uid":45033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾啊聲 窮飛龍都上榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a449dd7bbf808fdb1f764672470744a0c309c5","tid":27840,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"阿聲 笑波子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843e3f960383e7244a77d4e9a03290533a820b6e","tid":27840,"uid":50899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:04:22.000Z","msg":"之前成班屌鬼話熊仔頭點解唔拍長片<br />\n出到黎咪又係短個d最多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係高登少數定班人講一套做一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3737849dad927314183f6c6becca2e82f2c68b","tid":27840,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前成班屌鬼話熊仔頭點解唔拍長片<br />\n<br />\n出到黎咪又係短個d最多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係高登少數定班人講一套做一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇咩阿聲咩笑波子咩藍絲BOMBA咁多人睇就知咩事啦<br />\n小學雞鬼會同你睇長片"},{"pid":"462323ac4efff1073e572ecb040d1a8186c84ecc","tid":27840,"uid":36788,"like":0,"d